The paper discusses a new approximation algorithm for Real Time Recurrent Learning (RTRL), which is a popular training method for Recurrent Neural Networks (RNNs). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), which is the primary focus of the paper. Other likely sub-categories include cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.SY (Systems and Control). These sub-categories are relevant because the paper deals with RNNs, which are used in natural language processing, control systems, and other AI applications.
